方法三
执行test3()时，控制台输出如下：
...
getAddress: Thread[ForkJoinPool.commonPool-worker-1,5,main] -> 耗时: 157
getAddress: Thread[ForkJoinPool.commonPool-worker-2,5,main] -> 耗时: 46
getAddress: Thread[main,5,main] -> 耗时: 53
